  </div>

  <div id="painter-description" class="tabcontent">
    <p>Create beautiful art on a 3D canvas. Use multiple brush colours, the world grid
    and guide grid to create anything you can imagine. This game runs on desktop as well
    as mobile and will soon support multiplayer for people who want to paint together.
    Uses hardware accelerated graphics all from the comfort of your web browser. </p>
  </div>

  <div id="painter-code" class="tabcontent">
    <p>Technologies used: WebGL, Javascript, Three.js, Heroku</p>
    <p><a href="https://github.com/dbzguy56/portfolio/blob/3d_painter_setup/app/assets/javascripts/painter.js"
      target="_blank">
      Logic can be found here.</a></p>
